度浑浊，眼压：双5.5/4=20.55mmHg，故诊断&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:; font-size: 12pt; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal;&quot;&gt;双眼初发期白内&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:; font-size: 12pt; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal;&quot;&gt;障、2右眼眼底动脉硬化成立。据患者头颅MR：&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;右侧侧脑室后角旁腔隙性脑梗死&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: SimSun; font-size: 12pt; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:; font-size: 12pt; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:; font-size: 12pt; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: SimSun; font-size: 12pt; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:; font-size: 12pt; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:; font-size: 12pt; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: SimSun; font-size: 12pt; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:; font-size: 12pt; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:; font-size: 12pt; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:; font-size: 12pt; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal;&quot;&gt;，故诊断腔隙性脑梗死成立。入院后&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: SimSun; font-size: 12pt; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal;&quot;&gt;给予阿司匹林抗血小&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:; font-size: 12pt; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal;&quot;&gt;

